ective</a> and <a href=\"https://www.bonterratech.com/event/good-tech-fest-2023\">Bonterra</a>.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://goodtechfest.com/washington-dc/\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/04/GTF-DC-1.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1047\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/04/GTF-DC-1.jpg 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/04/GTF-DC-1.jpg 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2023/04/GTF-DC-1.jpg 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/04/GTF-DC-1.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://goodtechfest.com/washington-dc/\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Book your ticket</a></div><h3 id=\"how-to-fundraise-on-gitcoin\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/\">How to Fundraise on Gitcoin</a></h3><p><strong>(Apr 18, 3 PM UTC, Online - Zoom): </strong>as the <a href=\"https://grants.gitcoin.co/\">Gitcoin Grants Beta Round</a> is getting closer (starting on April 25th), join the next training of the Event Organizers' Guild where <a href=\"https://twitter.com/climateXcrypto\">John Ellison</a>, source at ReFi DAO, will give an overview of the best tips to run successful fundraising on Gitcoin. Check the Tweet for more info. 👇</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Less than 2 weeks until the start of the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/gitcoin?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@gitcoin</a> Beta Round! 🤯<br><br>Want to learn how to successfully fundraise through Gitcoin? Join <a href=\"https://twitter.com/climateXcrypto?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@climateXcrypto</a> for a training at the Event Organizers Guild!<br><br>📅 April 18<br>🕚 11 AM UTC or 🕒 3 PM UTC<br>📍 Zoom<br><br>Calendar invite below 👇<br>/1 <a href=\"https://t.co/npBpWjC5Kp\">pic.twitter.com/npBpWjC5Kp</a></p>&mdash; ReFi Spring 🤝 ReFi DAO (@RefiSpring) <a h